Title: We met in general compartment
DateModified: '2019-03-01'
DatePublished: '2019-03-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/we-met-in-general-compartment
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Arpita Dey
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I was waiting for my train then i saw i guy over there was trying to make eye
  cntact with me i just ignored then train came n i got seat thn i saw that guy was
  standing over there i just passed a smile this time train was about to leave the
  station the guy without any thoght just came up n sat in front of me n said hi ,,
  after some conversation i found out he has diffrent train ticket just becz of me
  without any thought he just came up i laughed n he was from diffrent city he dont
  know about anything i just saved him from ticket cheker , the journey was near about
  3 hours we became friend so easily he ask me to come his place n ask me to show
  my city also i told him about our culture our city he aded me on facebook he took
  my number as he was new to in kolkata i booked a cab for him next day we met for
  coffee we cahatted a lot i took him to kolkata's few popular places took some photos
  for memories we enjoyed a lot after one day he left this city.. Its been 3 years
  we didnt met again we are still in touch .. He call me radio city girl because i
  had journalism as my subject n i call him mr engnieer
